Package bulut

Interface Service

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.rmi.Remote
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BulutServer

    public interface Service
extends java.rmi.Remote
    An interface for Java RMI to support graph operations as well as loading balance for the user.
